'''Beyond Bree J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar 1992''' was published by the [[American Mensa Tolkien Special Interest Group]] and edited by [[Nancy Martsch]]. The calendar features black and white illustrations by six different artists inspired by [[The Silmarillion]].
